    "Any required evidence item remains pending, failed, blocked, or missing.",
    "Any required artifact lacks a digest before packaging the final evidence bundle.",
    "Any probe silently falls back to local/process memory for a production-shared target.",
    "Any manifest contains plaintext secrets instead of redacted secret references.",
    "Any observability dashboard or operator runbook fails to expose runtime/shared-authority truth and stop conditions.",
